            * u_xlat1.x;\n    u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_2.x + -0.00100000005;\n   
            u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * u_xlat16_2.xxxx;\n    SV_Target0 = u_xlat16_0;\n   
            u_xlatb1 = u_xlat16_5<0.0;\n    if(u_xlatb1){discard;}\n    return;\n}\n\n"
